        <h3 id="install_hydra">
            Install Hydra with Bower
        </h3>
        <p>
            To install Hydra as a Bower component you need to install it in your project using:
            <div>
                <pre><code class="language-javascript">bower install hydrajs</code></pre>
            </div>
            After installing Hydra in your project you can access it in your browser using:
            <div>
                <pre><code class="language-markup">&lt;script type="text/javascript" src="bower_components/hydrajs/versions/hydra.js"></script></code></pre>
            </div>
        </p>
